Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\a6}To think something like this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\a6}It's no use, Mr. Glover.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\a6}I have one of these too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}With that, the magistrate's office'll happily arrest you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}If that happens, the business and the Satchō Alliance'll be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Don't worry! I, Sakamoto Ryōma, shall clear any doubts on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:45.02,Thoughts,,10,10,0,,{\be6}Vivid summer memories surpass their season to solve mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:47.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be6}A Bakumatsu period drama set in Nagasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:49.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be6}Where is the missing scriptwriter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be6}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:52.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be6}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:54.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be6}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:51.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be6}Did we travel back in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be6}Nah.
